00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:39,650 --> 00:01:45,759
[Follow Your Heart]

3
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:04,979
[Episode 21]

4
00:02:05,090 --> 00:02:08,490
[Jingsheng Hall]

5
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:30,330
Why are you all at my house?

6
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:34,050
What happened to my face?

7
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:35,090
Surprise!

8
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:37,570
You don't need to wear your mask anymore.

9
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:39,590
My nose!

10
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,150
I performed

11
00:02:41,170 --> 00:02:42,829
plastic surgery on your nose.

12
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:43,870
Plastic surgery!

13
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:44,590
You...

14
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:45,790
You...

15
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:50,680
You...

16
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,550
Jiang Xinbai!

17
00:02:56,829 --> 00:02:57,350
Don't think

18
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:58,520
that you can decide everything for me

19
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,450
just because we've become allies!

20
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:01,790
Why are you

21
00:03:01,790 --> 00:03:02,829
only scolding me?

22
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,110
Get out!

23
00:03:04,490 --> 00:03:06,430
From now on, we'll stay out of each other's business.

24
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:07,160
Yan Nanxing.

25
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,230
His nose is fixed,

26
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:10,920
but he has lost his mind.

27
00:03:11,329 --> 00:03:12,079
All of you, get out!

28
00:03:12,079 --> 00:03:13,340
I don't want to see you!

29
00:03:14,350 --> 00:03:15,370
Could you please

30
00:03:15,410 --> 00:03:16,330
excuse us?

31
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:18,510
Okay.

32
00:03:33,860 --> 00:03:34,550
Bieli.

33
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,079
Gaya and I hope

34
00:03:38,110 --> 00:03:39,840
you can let go of your obsession

35
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,990
and stop wearing your mask.

36
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,120
Brother.

37
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,670
Gaya is gone.

38
00:03:52,670 --> 00:03:53,730
You should move on,

39
00:03:55,270 --> 00:03:56,230
and so should I.

40
00:04:41,540 --> 00:04:42,460
Mr. Shang,

41
00:04:42,910 --> 00:04:44,310
you're a great hero.

42
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:46,700
You can definitely pull yourself together.

43
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,000
No matter what happens,

44
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,409
I'll be with you.

45
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,070
Mr. Shang.

46
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,550
Did you stay up all night?

47
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,440
Sai'er.

48
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,550
Go somewhere with me.

49
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:29,470
Gaya.

50
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:31,600
This mask

51
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:34,040
is made of the ore from your hometown.

52
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:36,700
It carries your love for your hometown.

53
00:06:37,110 --> 00:06:38,120
I buried it here

54
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:42,630
facing your hometown.

55
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:45,930
When you get homesick,

56
00:06:46,790 --> 00:06:48,120
look into the distance.

57
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:52,280
I will protect Brother.

58
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,560
Please bless him

59
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,800
and keep him safe.

60
00:06:59,070 --> 00:06:59,670
Gaya.

61
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:06,610
I'm not coming here again.

62
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:12,620
I'm moving on.

63
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:21,950
Lady Gaya,

64
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:25,060
please bless Mr. Shang.

65
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:49,240
[Steps Towards Success]

66
00:08:12,770 --> 00:08:13,960
There's no need to clean this place today.

67
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,760
You may leave.

68
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:18,880
Chancellor.

69
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:20,180
Why are you here?

70
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:21,230
I'm here to...

71
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:22,200
You followed me?

72
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:25,150
Why would I?

73
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,060
Since you knew my name,

74
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,350
you could find out

75
00:08:28,350 --> 00:08:30,140
that I'm a chancellor at the Imperial Academy.

76
00:08:30,140 --> 00:08:30,950
You came here

77
00:08:31,030 --> 00:08:32,270
to make me notice you.

78
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:34,200
That's not true.

79
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:36,220
I've seen many people like you,

80
00:08:36,220 --> 00:08:37,960
a calculating social climber.

81
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,670
Just give up.

82
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,450
Although I don't despise you because you're a slave,

83
00:08:42,450 --> 00:08:43,390
it doesn't mean

84
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:44,390
I'll like you.

85
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:02,200
This...

86
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:03,620
This is my uniform.

87
00:09:04,430 --> 00:09:05,830
I'm supposed to be here.

88
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:08,800
You passed out that day.

89
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:10,880
I took you home to let you rest.

90
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:12,170
I didn't know you were a chancellor

91
00:09:12,170 --> 00:09:13,830
until we had dinner together.

92
00:09:14,470 --> 00:09:15,890
But I had no other intentions after I found out,

93
00:09:15,890 --> 00:09:17,200
nor did I think too much.

94
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:17,870
I just thought of the meal

95
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:19,180
as entertaining a friend

96
00:09:19,180 --> 00:09:20,180
at home.

97
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:21,480
A friend?

98
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,230
You

99
00:09:26,630 --> 00:09:27,830
consider me a friend?

100
00:09:28,230 --> 00:09:28,630
Yes.

101
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:29,640
A friend.

102
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:35,470
Do you know

103
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:37,020
what kind of friends I need?

104
00:09:38,260 --> 00:09:40,060
What kind of friends do you need?

105
00:09:41,430 --> 00:09:42,790
Only those who can

106
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,160
always stay by my side

107
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:45,630
and be my people

108
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:47,280
no matter what happens

109
00:09:47,710 --> 00:09:48,710
can be my friends.

110
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,910
Be your people?

111
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:00,380
So,

112
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:02,350
stop saying

113
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:03,750
that you can be my friend.

114
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:06,830
It has nothing to do

115
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:09,510
with whether you're a slave or not.

116
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:11,750
Suoluo.

117
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:16,950
Dean Yan.

118
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,320
Dean Yan.

119
00:10:22,050 --> 00:10:23,720
I asked you to clean this place up.

120
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,920
How dare you slack off

121
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,870
and disturb the chancellor?

122
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:30,110
You asked him to clean this place up?

123
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:32,910
Yes.

124
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,730
His name is Liu Ruoqian.

125
00:10:35,730 --> 00:10:37,470
He's the slave student the Imperial Academy

126
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:39,000
made an exception to admit.

127
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:39,980
He told us

128
00:10:40,230 --> 00:10:41,830
he wanted to work in order to earn tuition.

129
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:42,690
So, we asked him

130
00:10:42,710 --> 00:10:44,190
to do some physical labor.

131
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:48,270
However,

132
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:50,750
as a slave,

133
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:53,660
you're not qualified to take the imperial exams

134
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,260
and can never be an official.

135
00:10:55,700 --> 00:10:57,230
What's the use of studying

136
00:10:57,470 --> 00:10:58,870
at the Imperial Academy?

137
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:02,030
Why are you still standing here?

138
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:02,670
Go away.

139
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:06,190
Is becoming an official the only purpose of study?

140
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:08,270
People study to make themselves

141
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:09,030
upright,

142
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:11,330
well-mannered, and benevolent.

143
00:11:12,430 --> 00:11:13,830
Dean Yan, as a teacher,

144
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,600
how can you judge your student

145
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,260
based on traditional values?

146
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:22,230
I didn't mean to humiliate him.

147
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,030
I just wanted

148
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,360
to teach him some rules.

149
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:25,160
Chancellor.

150
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,190
Dean Yan.

151
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,700
Please don't argue about me.

152
00:11:30,710 --> 00:11:31,770
Since I was a child,

153
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:33,020
I've heard many humiliating words

154
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:34,070
like this.

155
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:36,780
If I cared about these words,

156
00:11:36,930 --> 00:11:39,590
I wouldn't be studying at the Imperial Academy.

157
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:41,470
Although I'm a slave,

158
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:43,350
I'm not ashamed of it.

159
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:45,680
No matter what others say,

160
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:46,880
it can't hurt me.

161
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:49,240
I'll take my leave.

162
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:57,310
Suoluo.

163
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,070
Give some of my salary

164
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:00,070
to Liu Ruoqian

165
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:01,310
as his pay.

166
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:02,870
Don't tell him it's from me.

167
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:04,440
Just tell him he got a pay rise.

168
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,000
Suoluo.

169
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,280
You are too kind!

170
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,920
-He‘s just a slave...
-We're at the Imperial Academy.

171
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,450
Please call me Chancellor.

172
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:15,150
Yes.

173
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:16,520
Chancellor.

174
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:21,000
I brought you some fresh fruit.

175
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:22,410
No, thanks.

176
00:12:22,990 --> 00:12:24,250
I have something to do.

177
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:36,770
[Shang Residence]

178
00:12:47,020 --> 00:12:49,250
Although your nose has grown back,

179
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,120
it will take some time

180
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:52,870
to get your sense of smell back.

181
00:12:56,310 --> 00:12:57,030
It's okay.

182
00:12:57,210 --> 00:12:58,190
I got this.

183
00:12:58,510 --> 00:12:59,230
I will get

184
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:01,030
Mr. Shang's sense of smell back.

185
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:02,610
I never owe anyone.

186
00:13:03,090 --> 00:13:04,430
If there's anything you want me to do,

187
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:05,360
just let me know.

188
00:13:08,310 --> 00:13:09,550
Don't mind if I do.

189
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,390
Actually,

190
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,190
I want you

191
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:14,530
to find someone for me.

192
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:15,990
I know who you want to find.

193
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:16,390
Boss,

194
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:16,950
you want to find

195
00:13:16,950 --> 00:13:18,550
the boy who saved you, right?

196
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,770
The Inspection Office

197
00:13:21,950 --> 00:13:22,590
is better

198
00:13:22,610 --> 00:13:24,590
at finding people than the Jinwu Guards.

199
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:26,920
Why don't you ask Jiang Xinbai to help you?

200
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,590
I don't want him

201
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:30,710
to worry about this anymore.

202
00:13:31,350 --> 00:13:31,910
So,

203
00:13:31,940 --> 00:13:33,400
I can only ask you for help.

204
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:35,070
Okay.

205
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:37,470
Thank you.

206
00:13:52,840 --> 00:14:00,800
Bravo!

207
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:13,640
Chancellor.

208
00:14:15,710 --> 00:14:16,440
Chancellor.

209
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:19,200
We meet by chance this time.

210
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:20,620
I didn't follow you.

211
00:14:20,860 --> 00:14:21,470
I know.

212
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:23,220
I misjudged you

213
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:25,070
at the Imperial Academy today.

214
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:27,260
Don't worry about it.

215
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:28,800
I really don't mind it.

216
00:14:31,230 --> 00:14:31,870
Chancellor.

217
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:32,870
Let me take these.

218
00:14:33,470 --> 00:14:34,070
Thank you.

219
00:14:39,270 --> 00:14:40,000
Chancellor.

220
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:42,100
Someone from the academy told me

221
00:14:42,100 --> 00:14:43,300
you gave me a pay rise.

222
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:44,790
Thank you.

223
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:46,640
You deserve it.

224
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,780
Are you going this way too?

225
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:55,390
I'm carrying these books for you.

226
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,520
Let me walk with you.

227
00:14:56,820 --> 00:14:57,950
Where are you going?

228
00:14:58,220 --> 00:14:59,870
I'm going to the bookstore.

229
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,370
Then I'll go to the bookstore with you.

230
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,630
It's late.

231
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:30,350
Why isn't he back yet?

232
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:35,410
Even if he doesn't want to come home for dinner, he should change his dressing.

233
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,080
Ms. Yan.

234
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:09,690
Where is your lord?

235
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,380
He's been reading the file

236
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:12,290
on Li Wufang's case

237
00:16:12,290 --> 00:16:13,750
in the file room since noon.

238
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:14,510
You can go in.

239
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:15,630
I'll stay out.

240
00:16:15,830 --> 00:16:16,430
Thank you.

241
00:16:23,470 --> 00:16:25,240
You only care

242
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:26,180
about the case.

243
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:29,560
Why didn't you go home early to change your dressing?

244
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:30,910
Sit still.

245
00:16:38,590 --> 00:16:39,250
Let's do it.

246
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:41,550
What's wrong?

247
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:45,290
What are you doing?

248
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,760
Taking off your clothes.

249
00:16:47,850 --> 00:16:50,710
How can I change your dressing with your clothes on?

250
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,390
I don't think it's appropriate.

251
00:16:52,390 --> 00:16:53,830
What are you shy about?

252
00:16:54,190 --> 00:16:54,830
I also

253
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:56,510
changed your dressing at home.

254
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:58,150
We're not at home after all.

255
00:16:58,650 --> 00:17:00,450
We're at the Inspection Office.

256
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,310
What are you afraid of?

257
00:17:02,310 --> 00:17:03,710
There's no one else here.

258
00:17:04,990 --> 00:17:05,670
Anyway...

259
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:06,680
Anyway...

260
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:09,280
This feels strange.

261
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:12,830
You're so troublesome.

262
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:19,510
Okay.

263
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:21,410
Let's get started.

264
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,000
What now?

265
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:27,990
Actually,

266
00:17:30,089 --> 00:17:31,000
my wound

267
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,060
has almost healed.

268
00:17:32,910 --> 00:17:33,720
I knew it.

269
00:17:35,910 --> 00:17:37,430
If you don't want to change your dressing,

270
00:17:37,430 --> 00:17:39,960
you should at least take the oral medication.

271
00:17:40,630 --> 00:17:41,430
Luckily,

272
00:17:41,450 --> 00:17:42,250
I was smart.

273
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:45,230
See? I've prepared it.

274
00:17:48,950 --> 00:17:49,480
Alright.

275
00:17:50,470 --> 00:17:51,730
It hasn't turned cold.

276
00:17:52,030 --> 00:17:52,430
Here.

277
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:53,440
Let me feed you.

278
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:56,060
It's not hot anymore.

279
00:17:56,500 --> 00:17:57,760
I'll blow on it for you.

280
00:18:05,630 --> 00:18:06,150
Okay.

281
00:18:06,750 --> 00:18:07,680
It's cooler now.

282
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:08,750
Wait.

283
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:20,630
I see.

284
00:18:21,150 --> 00:18:22,950
Is Chief Constable Jiang

285
00:18:23,230 --> 00:18:24,150
afraid

286
00:18:25,300 --> 00:18:26,590
of bitterness?

287
00:18:32,190 --> 00:18:34,060
Who said I'm afraid of bitterness?

288
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:34,860
Then drink it.

289
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:43,920
Drink it.

290
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:56,470
Here.

291
00:19:05,500 --> 00:19:07,300
The bitter taste is gone, right?

292
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:13,720
♫Sit with you at night and listen to the wind♫

293
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:15,020
Yes.

294
00:19:14,490 --> 00:19:17,150
♫When the wind flutters, the heart does too♫

295
00:19:17,820 --> 00:19:20,770
♫Step by step, no words are spoken♫

296
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:24,740
♫Barged into sight♫

297
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:28,210
♫When did your figure grow hazy?♫

