00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:31,860
♫And how clear is it?♫

299
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:34,610
♫I don't intend to break your heart♫

300
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:37,820
♫Silently fall into my arms♫

301
00:19:43,670 --> 00:19:44,390
Mr. Yao.

302
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:45,790
Are you going home?

303
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:46,310
Yes.

304
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:46,950
Well,

305
00:19:46,990 --> 00:19:48,110
has Mr. Jiang gone home?

306
00:19:48,110 --> 00:19:48,990
It's very late.

307
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,310
I think he has gone home.

308
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:51,870
Take a look around and lock the door.

309
00:19:51,870 --> 00:19:52,390
Okay.

310
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,030
You were so stupid.

311
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:02,880
You went there

312
00:20:03,060 --> 00:20:05,230
just because Li Wufang asked you to?

313
00:20:07,430 --> 00:20:08,560
What else could I do?

314
00:20:09,670 --> 00:20:11,270
I couldn't just watch you get hurt

315
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,300
and do nothing.

316
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,330
What if he was trying to scare you?

317
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:16,990
What if I was fine?

318
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:18,860
I couldn't take the risk.

319
00:20:31,470 --> 00:20:32,230
Back then,

320
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:35,460
when my father was investigating

321
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:36,620
the Zornia case,

322
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:38,860
he found

323
00:20:38,890 --> 00:20:40,350
a very important witness.

324
00:20:41,940 --> 00:20:43,800
As long as the witness testified,

325
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:45,310
he could have removed

326
00:20:45,330 --> 00:20:47,250
the force behind the Zornia.

327
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:50,790
However,

328
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:53,550
the night before the witness testified

329
00:20:53,550 --> 00:20:55,150
against the Zornia gang,

330
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:57,750
the witness died.

331
00:20:59,180 --> 00:21:00,780
His whole family was killed.

332
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,160
Was the murderer found?

333
00:21:10,210 --> 00:21:11,180
This matter

334
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:14,070
became my father's lifelong pain.

335
00:21:15,230 --> 00:21:16,030
That witness

336
00:21:16,810 --> 00:21:18,340
had the same surname as you.

337
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:19,920
His surname was Yan too.

338
00:21:20,630 --> 00:21:22,090
His name was Yan Zhizhong.

339
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:26,190
Actually...

340
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:29,260
Actually, my surname is not Yan.

341
00:21:29,790 --> 00:21:30,710
My mother said

342
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:32,230
she named me

343
00:21:32,250 --> 00:21:33,180
after my savior.

344
00:21:33,390 --> 00:21:34,520
His surname was Yan.

345
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:44,230
Yan Nanxing.

346
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:46,070
Although

347
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:49,080
you're not related to Yan Zhizhong,

348
00:21:49,520 --> 00:21:51,650
and although you are not my witness...

349
00:21:51,870 --> 00:21:52,550
Whenever I

350
00:21:53,790 --> 00:21:54,990
think of how

351
00:21:55,630 --> 00:21:56,880
Li Wufang kidnapped you

352
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,210
and forced me to submit,

353
00:21:58,310 --> 00:21:59,370
whenever I think of

354
00:22:01,430 --> 00:22:02,910
how you almost got hurt

355
00:22:03,190 --> 00:22:04,270
because of me,

356
00:22:06,630 --> 00:22:07,860
whenever I think of...

357
00:22:07,860 --> 00:22:08,860
But I trust you.

358
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:12,410
I believe

359
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:14,050
you are no longer

360
00:22:14,050 --> 00:22:15,710
the Jiang Xinbai from before.

361
00:22:15,950 --> 00:22:16,820
Now,

362
00:22:17,430 --> 00:22:19,360
you can save the people from danger

363
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:21,990
and rescue every person in front of you.

364
00:22:22,950 --> 00:22:24,280
You can also protect me.

365
00:22:38,290 --> 00:22:39,420
I will.

366
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:52,180
Are you hungry?

367
00:22:53,350 --> 00:22:54,670
Let's go home and eat.

368
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:56,270
I feel so hungry.

369
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:03,550
Why is the door locked?

370
00:23:06,630 --> 00:23:07,520
Is anyone here?

371
00:23:09,910 --> 00:23:10,990
Is anyone here?

372
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:14,480
I think it was locked from the outside.

373
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:17,220
What should we do?

374
00:23:22,100 --> 00:23:22,830
Don't worry.

375
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,870
Tomorrow is the Doors Open Day.

376
00:23:24,870 --> 00:23:25,710
It will open

377
00:23:25,710 --> 00:23:26,980
two hours earlier than usual.

378
00:23:26,980 --> 00:23:28,440
What is the Doors Open Day?

379
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,460
The Inspection Office

380
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:36,990
has a Doors Open Day

381
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,590
on the 1st and 15th of each month.

382
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:39,520
We open our doors

383
00:23:39,950 --> 00:23:41,550
and if the common people

384
00:23:41,630 --> 00:23:42,580
have any injustices,

385
00:23:42,580 --> 00:23:44,230
they can come and complain.

386
00:23:45,170 --> 00:23:47,090
Let's make do with it tonight.

387
00:23:47,390 --> 00:23:48,190
Tomorrow,

388
00:23:48,870 --> 00:23:49,470
as soon as

389
00:23:49,630 --> 00:23:50,490
the door opens,

390
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:52,910
I'll take you to eat something delicious.

391
00:23:57,550 --> 00:23:58,350
Okay.

392
00:24:03,470 --> 00:24:04,510
But

393
00:24:05,670 --> 00:24:06,550
we...

394
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:35,030
I know

395
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:37,020
you want to protect me,

396
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,830
but I still hope

397
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:42,890
that if you face any difficulties

398
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:45,700
you can face it with me in the future.

399
00:24:47,150 --> 00:24:48,510
Don't bear everything

400
00:24:49,910 --> 00:24:51,430
or make decisions

401
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:53,430
all by yourself.

402
00:24:54,830 --> 00:24:56,360
You should at least tell me.

403
00:24:58,310 --> 00:24:59,150
Okay?

404
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:04,070
Okay?

405
00:25:05,230 --> 00:25:06,390
I'm talking to you.

406
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:10,200
Are you asleep?

407
00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:12,650
Don't pretend to be asleep.

408
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:14,010
I'm not gullible.

409
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,770
Are you really asleep?

410
00:25:41,930 --> 00:25:42,990
You're injured

411
00:25:44,510 --> 00:25:46,110
and you still worked so hard.

412
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:50,860
You must be tired.

413
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,440
Why are you so pretty?

414
00:28:13,950 --> 00:28:17,710
[Guangyu Hall]

415
00:28:20,190 --> 00:28:20,790
Zhiyi,

416
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:22,440
you can't sleep at all

417
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,110
for so many nights.

418
00:28:23,110 --> 00:28:23,910
This can't do.

419
00:28:24,120 --> 00:28:25,570
It breaks my heart to see it.

420
00:28:25,570 --> 00:28:26,100
How about

421
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,390
we call an imperial physician for a checkup?

422
00:28:28,390 --> 00:28:29,470
What for?

423
00:28:29,950 --> 00:28:31,320
When I entered the palace yesterday,

424
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,380
Her Majesty told me

425
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:33,670
that half a month ago,

426
00:28:33,670 --> 00:28:34,930
Xinbai and Shang Bieli

427
00:28:35,060 --> 00:28:36,670
were both called by His Majesty.

428
00:28:36,670 --> 00:28:38,530
His Majesty even lost his temper.

429
00:28:38,670 --> 00:28:39,190
I wonder

430
00:28:39,190 --> 00:28:40,190
what happened.

431
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:42,570
Just thinking about it makes me nervous.

432
00:28:42,630 --> 00:28:43,550
It hurts.

433
00:28:43,710 --> 00:28:44,810
I didn't do anything.

434
00:28:44,810 --> 00:28:45,670
It still hurts.

435
00:28:45,750 --> 00:28:46,910
Okay, it's my fault.

436
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:52,840
Don't worry.

437
00:28:53,030 --> 00:28:54,440
It's been a long time since then.

438
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,300
It will be fine.

439
00:28:55,730 --> 00:28:57,430
Being with a king is like being with a tiger.

440
00:28:57,430 --> 00:28:58,710
You know how Xinbai is.

441
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:00,030
Since childhood,

442
00:29:00,030 --> 00:29:01,190
he only tells us good news.

443
00:29:01,190 --> 00:29:01,810
We don't even know

444
00:29:01,810 --> 00:29:02,720
what happened.

445
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:04,150
We can't help at all.

446
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:06,750
How about

447
00:29:06,750 --> 00:29:08,200
I go to the Inspection Office

448
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:09,460
and ask what happened?

449
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:10,630
No.

450
00:29:11,540 --> 00:29:12,460
It's been so many days

451
00:29:12,460 --> 00:29:14,190
and he hasn't even come to see me.

452
00:29:14,190 --> 00:29:15,310
Why would you go to see him?

453
00:29:15,310 --> 00:29:15,840
Don't go.

454
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:17,510
Fine.

455
00:29:17,530 --> 00:29:18,210
I won't go.

456
00:29:20,540 --> 00:29:21,560
Is today

457
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:23,850
the Inspection Office's Doors Open Day?

458
00:29:25,470 --> 00:29:26,230
Don’t move. It’s not done yet.

459
00:29:26,230 --> 00:29:27,630
I'm going to report my son

460
00:29:27,670 --> 00:29:28,710
and say my son is unfilial

461
00:29:28,710 --> 00:29:29,950
and shows off at home.

462
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:30,580
So early?

463
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:31,840
I'm done.

464
00:29:31,870 --> 00:29:32,710
You need to look proper.

465
00:29:32,710 --> 00:29:33,710
It's not done yet.

466
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:35,480
I won't. I'll just be improper.

467
00:29:43,430 --> 00:29:43,950
My lord.

468
00:29:44,910 --> 00:29:45,430
My lord?

469
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:49,030
My lord,

470
00:29:49,650 --> 00:29:51,110
why did you two sleep here?

471
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:01,590
Don't tell anyone

472
00:30:01,690 --> 00:30:02,450
about this.

473
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:04,680
It's too late.

474
00:30:11,770 --> 00:30:12,540
Right? Look.

475
00:30:12,940 --> 00:30:13,490
Yes.

476
00:30:22,630 --> 00:30:23,470
I can explain.

477
00:30:23,490 --> 00:30:23,950
Shut up.

478
00:30:26,870 --> 00:30:27,400
Speak up.

479
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:31,210
Speak up.

480
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:32,880
Speak up.

481
00:30:40,970 --> 00:30:41,850
Mr. Jiang,

482
00:30:42,050 --> 00:30:42,860
what's going on

483
00:30:42,860 --> 00:30:44,620
between you and Ms. Yan?

484
00:30:44,910 --> 00:30:45,790
Are you two

485
00:30:45,810 --> 00:30:47,030
together?

486
00:30:47,390 --> 00:30:48,750
Is the rumor true?

487
00:30:50,330 --> 00:30:51,280
We have to face

488
00:30:51,490 --> 00:30:52,490
what we must face.

489
00:30:56,730 --> 00:30:57,790
Zhiyi!

490
00:30:58,170 --> 00:30:59,290
Don't be angry.

491
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:00,310
Zhiyi.

492
00:31:08,230 --> 00:31:08,830
Let go!

493
00:31:16,490 --> 00:31:17,220
Yan Nanxing.

494
00:31:19,430 --> 00:31:20,030
It's okay.

495
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:21,990
No matter what happens,

496
00:31:22,460 --> 00:31:23,790
we'll face it together.

497
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:24,870
I...

498
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:28,720
Didn't she leave the capital?

499
00:31:29,370 --> 00:31:30,350
Were you hiding her

500
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,310
these days?

501
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:32,350
Yes.

502
00:31:33,070 --> 00:31:34,000
During this period,

503
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:34,790
Yan Nanxing

504
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,410
has been living in my house.

505
00:31:38,850 --> 00:31:40,090
She is a traveler,

506
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:42,790
but she's been freeloading off of you.

507
00:31:42,790 --> 00:31:43,590
What else

508
00:31:44,910 --> 00:31:46,030
have you two done?

509
00:31:47,110 --> 00:31:47,870
We even—

510
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:50,130
We reconciled and patched things up.

511
00:31:57,870 --> 00:31:59,800
I want to talk to Yan Nanxing alone.

512
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:00,990
Get out.

513
00:32:10,010 --> 00:32:10,940
Will you be okay?

514
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,270
Sure.

515
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:21,610
Have a good chat.

516
00:32:23,210 --> 00:32:24,160
Don't worry.

517
00:32:24,700 --> 00:32:26,450
I won't do anything stupid.

518
00:32:28,150 --> 00:32:28,710
Go.

519
00:32:39,300 --> 00:32:40,430
You're not leaving?

520
00:33:07,470 --> 00:33:08,930
She almost discovered me.

521
00:33:10,150 --> 00:33:11,190
This girl

522
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:13,300
is quite similar to your mother.

523
00:33:13,730 --> 00:33:14,460
She's smart,

524
00:33:15,090 --> 00:33:15,840
gentle,

525
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:17,110
and kind.

526
00:33:18,530 --> 00:33:19,410
Right, Mr. Yan?

527
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:24,010
Name your price.

528
00:33:26,710 --> 00:33:27,550
What price?

529
00:33:29,870 --> 00:33:32,200
How much money do you need to leave Xinbai?

530
00:33:35,620 --> 00:33:36,740
I didn't expect

531
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:38,710
such cliche words

532
00:33:38,990 --> 00:33:40,310
would come from

533
00:33:40,310 --> 00:33:41,110
the princess.

534
00:33:42,280 --> 00:33:43,290
So tacky.

535
00:33:43,470 --> 00:33:44,730
You're too shy to do it?

536
00:33:45,360 --> 00:33:45,840
Fine.

537
00:33:46,630 --> 00:33:48,160
I'll name the price for you.

538
00:33:48,230 --> 00:33:49,390
One hundred taels of gold

539
00:33:49,390 --> 00:33:51,330
is enough for you to live a good life.

540
00:33:51,330 --> 00:33:52,080
As long as you leave,

541
00:33:52,080 --> 00:33:53,540
I'll pay you immediately.

542
00:34:04,370 --> 00:34:05,190
What is this?

543
00:34:05,800 --> 00:34:07,870
You said you would give me 100 taels of gold,

544
00:34:07,870 --> 00:34:09,470
but I don't see anything yet.

545
00:34:09,500 --> 00:34:10,740
I'm different.

546
00:34:10,950 --> 00:34:12,150
I'm a woman of my word.

547
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:13,460
I'll give it to you now.

548
00:34:14,350 --> 00:34:15,630
Since I promised you,

549
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,780
I will reward you with gold

550
00:34:17,990 --> 00:34:19,120
as long as you leave.

551
00:34:19,830 --> 00:34:21,560
If you give me 100 taels of gold,

552
00:34:21,990 --> 00:34:23,650
I'll give you 100 taels of gold

553
00:34:23,720 --> 00:34:24,850
and one copper coin.

554
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:27,510
If you give me 1,000 taels of gold,

555
00:34:27,530 --> 00:34:29,330
I'll give you 1,000 taels of gold

556
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:30,920
and one copper coin.

557
00:34:31,010 --> 00:34:31,530
You!

558
00:34:31,560 --> 00:34:33,290
I'll always give more than you.

559
00:34:39,590 --> 00:34:41,389
Why are they speaking nonsense?

560
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:43,000
Are they going to fight?

561
00:34:43,429 --> 00:34:45,230
Let them spill their hearts out.

562
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:46,940
Wait for them to

563
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:48,000
release their emotions.

564
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:48,719
After that,

565
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:50,600
everything will be doable.

566
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,190
That makes sense.

567
00:34:52,389 --> 00:34:53,449
Let's listen more.

568
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,909
You're a traitor.

569
00:34:54,929 --> 00:34:56,159
I treated you as my best friend,

570
00:34:56,159 --> 00:34:57,170
but you seduced my son

571
00:34:57,170 --> 00:34:58,080
and cheated me of my feelings.

572
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:58,989
How did I lie to you?

573
00:34:58,989 --> 00:34:59,790
I met your son

574
00:34:59,790 --> 00:35:00,310
before I met you.

575
00:35:00,310 --> 00:35:01,270
How did I lie?

576
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:01,960
You!

577
00:35:01,989 --> 00:35:02,800
What?

578
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:03,460
You said I was your close friend.

579
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:04,389
I'm not good enough for you.

580
00:35:04,389 --> 00:35:05,400
You are heartless.

581
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:05,960
They're fighting.

582
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:06,800
When did I ever look down on you?

583
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,790
Never.

584
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,659
You say you don't mind,

585
00:35:08,659 --> 00:35:09,409
but your feelings are honest.

586
00:35:09,409 --> 00:35:10,290
I'm your best friend when I say nice things.

587
00:35:10,290 --> 00:35:11,199
I'm heartless when I don't.

588
00:35:11,199 --> 00:35:12,010
You're such a wicked mother-in-law.

589
00:35:12,010 --> 00:35:12,310
Wicked...

590
00:35:12,310 --> 00:35:13,230
Wicked mother-in-law?

591
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,150
Wicked mother-in-law!

592
00:35:14,150 --> 00:35:14,630
Okay.

593
00:35:14,830 --> 00:35:16,410
I'll be the wicked mother-in-law.

594
00:35:16,410 --> 00:35:17,060
You hit me?

