00:35:21,710 --> 00:35:22,570
Wait a bit more.

596
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:23,630
I'm so worried.

597
00:35:23,630 --> 00:35:24,230
Just wait.

598
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:25,590
Okay.

599
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:30,120
Yan Nanxing!

600
00:35:30,190 --> 00:35:30,720
Hurry up!

601
00:35:31,310 --> 00:35:31,910
Let go!

602
00:35:31,930 --> 00:35:32,850
Let go!

603
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:35,080
-Enough, Yan Nanxing.
-Stop fighting!

604
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:36,230
Zhiyi!

605
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:37,190
Why are you fighting?

606
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:38,390
You are the princess.

607
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:39,520
What are you doing?

608
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:40,710
Are you helping me or her?

609
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:42,240
It has nothing to do with me.

610
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,110
Zhiyi.

611
00:35:55,710 --> 00:35:56,440
Can't sleep?

612
00:36:15,790 --> 00:36:16,590
What's wrong?

613
00:36:16,990 --> 00:36:17,950
I'm angry.

614
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,670
Actually,

615
00:36:21,830 --> 00:36:22,670
I’ve been thinking of Yan Nanxing

616
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:23,830
every day,

617
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:26,610
but she said those things about me.

618
00:36:26,830 --> 00:36:27,760
What did she say?

619
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,790
She said I only listen to what I want to hear.

620
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:32,020
She said I'm arrogant.

621
00:36:32,020 --> 00:36:33,550
She said I'm unreasonable.

622
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:36,090
She even said I'm a wicked mother-in-law.

623
00:36:36,390 --> 00:36:37,660
I'm not a wicked mother-in-law,

624
00:36:37,660 --> 00:36:38,110
right?

625
00:36:42,370 --> 00:36:44,170
Why aren't you saying anything?

626
00:36:49,530 --> 00:36:51,330
I'm not that kind of person, am I?

627
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:01,440
You're not usually like this.

628
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:02,470
But

629
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:05,210
you care more about the people and things

630
00:37:05,550 --> 00:37:06,950
around Xinbai.

631
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:09,110
Your concern makes you anxious,

632
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:09,640
so

633
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:11,000
you treat Yan Nanxing

634
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:13,430
a bit more strictly.

635
00:37:14,550 --> 00:37:15,590
Look,

636
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:17,350
so many people

637
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:19,040
saw Xinbai and Yan Nanxing

638
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:19,900
together today

639
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,670
and you made a scene too.

640
00:37:22,510 --> 00:37:24,140
Who knows what the people

641
00:37:25,010 --> 00:37:25,890
are saying

642
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:27,030
about this now?

643
00:37:28,950 --> 00:37:30,150
What should I do?

644
00:37:31,350 --> 00:37:32,590
I was just angry.

645
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:33,950
I couldn't help it.

646
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:36,360
Don't cry.

647
00:37:37,310 --> 00:37:38,270
It's okay.

648
00:37:40,610 --> 00:37:42,340
At most, those ignorant people

649
00:37:42,590 --> 00:37:43,950
will say

650
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:46,010
that Blossom Beauty closed

651
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:47,990
because you abused your power

652
00:37:48,390 --> 00:37:49,720
and bullied a commoner.

653
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:51,510
But it's okay.

654
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:52,970
How about this?

655
00:37:53,310 --> 00:37:54,800
Yan Nanxing is living with Xinbai

656
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:56,030
because she has nowhere to stay.

657
00:37:56,030 --> 00:37:56,950
In my opinion,

658
00:37:58,380 --> 00:38:01,230
you should let Yan Nanxing reopen Blossom Beauty.

659
00:38:02,790 --> 00:38:04,190
Suoluo told me already.

660
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:06,600
Xinbai has taken the title deed.

661
00:38:10,650 --> 00:38:12,040
How come even Suoluo

662
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:13,190
is biased

663
00:38:13,210 --> 00:38:14,240
toward her brother now?

664
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:15,150
That's good.

665
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:16,480
It's sibling love,

666
00:38:16,990 --> 00:38:17,630
right?

667
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:19,510
Fine.

668
00:38:20,550 --> 00:38:22,080
Blossom Beauty can reopen,

669
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:23,580
but Yan Nanxing

670
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:25,240
can never be my daughter-in-law.

671
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:25,810
Why?

672
00:38:26,430 --> 00:38:27,630
You don't understand.

673
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:28,310
When Xinbai

674
00:38:28,310 --> 00:38:30,110
went on a blind date with Ms. Pei,

675
00:38:30,110 --> 00:38:31,830
I asked Yan Nanxing to be the matchmaker.

676
00:38:31,830 --> 00:38:32,910
If Pei Linfu

677
00:38:32,940 --> 00:38:34,140
realizes that Xinbai

678
00:38:34,350 --> 00:38:35,710
brought his ex-wife

679
00:38:35,830 --> 00:38:37,140
on a date with his daughter

680
00:38:37,140 --> 00:38:38,340
and made up in the end,

681
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:40,350
he might get angry and treat Xinbai badly.

682
00:38:40,350 --> 00:38:41,610
Then what should we do?

683
00:38:43,550 --> 00:38:44,590
It's that complicated?

684
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,790
Yes, it's that complicated.

685
00:38:45,790 --> 00:38:47,080
Let's put Pei Linfu aside.

686
00:38:47,080 --> 00:38:48,360
Yan Nanxing herself

687
00:38:48,390 --> 00:38:49,630
is a troublemaker.

688
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:51,950
Xinbai is already treading on thin ice.

689
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:53,460
I can't let him be harmed by her.

690
00:38:53,460 --> 00:38:53,980
So,

691
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,060
I must break them up

692
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,880
and be a wicked mother-in-law.

693
00:38:58,830 --> 00:39:00,310
Why is love

694
00:39:00,330 --> 00:39:01,610
so hard?

695
00:39:01,990 --> 00:39:03,960
It's as hard as flying in the sky.

696
00:39:05,330 --> 00:39:06,200
I ask the world,

697
00:39:06,950 --> 00:39:08,470
what is love?

698
00:39:08,830 --> 00:39:09,460
I just—

699
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:09,870
All right.

700
00:39:09,870 --> 00:39:10,670
Stop talking.

701
00:39:11,540 --> 00:39:12,940
Just remember one thing.

702
00:39:13,230 --> 00:39:14,210
Keep an eye on Blossom Beauty.

703
00:39:14,210 --> 00:39:15,340
If anything happens,

704
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:16,540
tell me immediately.

705
00:39:20,690 --> 00:39:21,950
I'll keep an eye on her.

706
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,530
What happened to your face?

707
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:26,470
Who hit you?

708
00:39:26,930 --> 00:39:27,590
Let me see.

709
00:39:28,270 --> 00:39:29,070
Why is it so red?

710
00:39:29,070 --> 00:39:30,150
Is it five fingerprints?

711
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:30,550
Yes.

712
00:39:31,550 --> 00:39:33,350
Stretch out your hand and check.

713
00:39:33,430 --> 00:39:34,090
Compare it.

714
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:36,210
Isn't the size just right?

715
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,480
It wasn't me.

716
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:39,710
You're playing dumb.

717
00:39:52,910 --> 00:39:54,910
You haven't eaten anything all day.

718
00:39:54,950 --> 00:39:55,990
Eat some first.

719
00:39:56,950 --> 00:39:58,270
These drumsticks and scallion pancakes

720
00:39:58,270 --> 00:39:59,600
are all your favorites.

721
00:40:05,630 --> 00:40:07,360
I didn't come to save you in time

722
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:09,230
because I wanted to give you two some space

723
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:10,070
to

724
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:12,530
vent your anger

725
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,850
and be honest with each other.

726
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:16,750
What trick is this?

727
00:40:22,110 --> 00:40:23,270
To be honest,

728
00:40:23,590 --> 00:40:25,070
it's good that you two

729
00:40:25,390 --> 00:40:26,650
made a scene like this.

730
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:27,760
How is it good?

731
00:40:28,610 --> 00:40:29,370
First,

732
00:40:29,790 --> 00:40:31,550
for the sake of the people,

733
00:40:31,870 --> 00:40:33,790
my mother won't target you anymore.

734
00:40:33,790 --> 00:40:34,430
Second,

735
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:36,750
since everyone knows

736
00:40:36,750 --> 00:40:38,030
about our relationship now,

737
00:40:38,030 --> 00:40:39,290
Yuejiang's Residence

738
00:40:39,390 --> 00:40:40,720
won't ignore it either.

739
00:40:41,630 --> 00:40:42,390
Li Wufang

740
00:40:42,660 --> 00:40:44,190
already has his eyes on you.

741
00:40:44,470 --> 00:40:45,180
This means

742
00:40:45,390 --> 00:40:46,590
the people behind him

743
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:47,840
will be after you too.

744
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:48,510
I'm afraid

745
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,750
I won't be able to

746
00:40:51,310 --> 00:40:53,040
protect you by myself anymore.

747
00:40:53,150 --> 00:40:54,670
So,

748
00:40:55,470 --> 00:40:57,550
you wanted us to make up

749
00:41:00,190 --> 00:41:01,470
and make it public

750
00:41:01,950 --> 00:41:03,030
so I can be

751
00:41:03,030 --> 00:41:05,090
protected by Yuejiang's Residence?

752
00:41:09,790 --> 00:41:10,470
Then

753
00:41:11,390 --> 00:41:12,230
is there

754
00:41:12,230 --> 00:41:13,230
any other reason?

755
00:41:15,710 --> 00:41:16,670
What other reasons do you think

756
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,530
there could be?

757
00:41:18,510 --> 00:41:19,510
You

758
00:41:19,530 --> 00:41:20,500
are so weird.

759
00:41:20,750 --> 00:41:21,680
How would I know?

760
00:41:22,430 --> 00:41:23,390
You're so smart.

761
00:41:23,830 --> 00:41:25,090
How could you not know?

762
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:26,110
I'm not smart.

763
00:41:26,230 --> 00:41:27,290
You have to tell me.

764
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:39,360
What is this?

765
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:43,780
Blossom Beauty can reopen.

766
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:45,810
Now that I'm your Boss,

767
00:41:46,070 --> 00:41:46,680
no one

768
00:41:47,110 --> 00:41:48,840
will dare to kick you out again.

769
00:41:49,510 --> 00:41:50,510
How did you get it?

770
00:41:51,670 --> 00:41:52,870
I have my own ways.

771
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,750
When Li Wufang

772
00:41:58,190 --> 00:41:59,740
arrested me that day,

773
00:42:01,020 --> 00:42:01,910
was this

774
00:42:02,150 --> 00:42:04,280
the important thing that you wanted to

775
00:42:05,190 --> 00:42:06,120
talk to me about?

776
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:13,790
Well...

777
00:42:14,910 --> 00:42:15,960
Well, thank you.

778
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:18,560
What do you mean "well, thank you"?

779
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:21,450
You're still unhappy?

780
00:42:23,070 --> 00:42:23,590
Wait.

781
00:42:26,930 --> 00:42:27,970
Look what this is.

782
00:42:28,990 --> 00:42:29,920
What is this now?

783
00:42:33,400 --> 00:42:34,830
I got the title deed

784
00:42:35,430 --> 00:42:36,690
of your residence too.

785
00:42:42,310 --> 00:42:42,750
You...

786
00:42:43,510 --> 00:42:44,430
You...

787
00:42:45,270 --> 00:42:46,350
really...

788
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:48,650
can do anything you want.

789
00:42:54,990 --> 00:42:55,790
No, Yan Nanxing.

790
00:42:55,790 --> 00:42:56,250
I'm not—

791
00:42:56,330 --> 00:42:57,660
I'm not kicking you out.

792
00:42:57,830 --> 00:42:58,760
Enough. Stop it.

793
00:43:01,150 --> 00:43:02,350
If you think

794
00:43:02,350 --> 00:43:03,020
you like living here,

795
00:43:03,020 --> 00:43:04,280
