796
00:43:04,330 --> 00:43:04,910
No need.

797
00:43:06,430 --> 00:43:07,560
I don't like it here.

798
00:43:08,150 --> 00:43:09,230
Anyway, you gave me

799
00:43:09,250 --> 00:43:10,650
the title and land deeds.

800
00:43:10,950 --> 00:43:11,680
Tomorrow...

801
00:43:11,910 --> 00:43:12,670
Tomorrow,

802
00:43:12,970 --> 00:43:13,870
I'll move back.

803
00:43:14,430 --> 00:43:15,360
No, Yan Nanxing.

804
00:43:15,910 --> 00:43:17,170
You haven't eaten yet.

805
00:43:22,150 --> 00:43:22,750
Thank you.

806
00:43:24,470 --> 00:43:25,110
Yan Nanxing!

